<subSubSection pageId="92" pageNumber="371" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="92.[178,1385,1758,2378]" pageId="92" pageNumber="371">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[181,535,2227,2260]" pageId="92" pageNumber="371">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List. Given the relatively restricted distribution and lack of biological knowledge, the Chiriquian Harvest Mouse should be carefully monitored.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
